{"tid":2410874,"cid":37,"subCid":0,"title":"太古城牛年首宗成交 套3房1780萬沽平手走 低估價35萬","createTime":"2021-02-17T03:09:43.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-17T15:25:30.000Z","uid":166360,"like":1,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"51fc15057875105e79c14d443e411bb5dfa46957","tid":2410874,"uid":166360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-17T03:09:43.000Z","msg":"太古城牛年首宗成交 套3房1780萬沽平手走 低估價35萬<br />\n10:28 2021/02/17<br />\n<br />\n&quot;......翠榕閣高層C室，實用面積897平方呎，套3房間隔，單位於1月初以1,800萬元放盤，終以1,780萬元沽出，累減20萬元，實用呎價19,844元。售價較銀行估價1823萬低35萬元。原業主於2018年2月以1780萬元購入，帳面平手離場，惟計算釐印費和律師費要蝕讓離場......&quot;<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://ps.hket.com/article/2878822/%E5%A4%AA%E5%8F%A4%E5%9F%8E%E7%89%9B%E5%B9%B4%E9%A6%96%E5%AE%97%E6%88%90%E4%BA%A4%20%E5%A5%973%E6%88%BF1780%E8%90%AC%E6%B2%BD%20%E4%BD%8E%E4%BC%B0%E5%83%B935%E8%90%AC?mtc=60037\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fps.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2878822%2F%25E5%25A4%25AA%25E5%258F%25A4%25E5%259F%258E%25E7%2589%259B%25E5%25B9%25B4%25E9%25A6%2596%25E5%25AE%2597%25E6%2588%2590%25E4%25BA%25A4%2520%25E5%25A5%25973%25E6%2588%25BF1780%25E8%2590%25AC%25E6%25B2%25BD%2520%25E4%25BD%258E%25E4%25BC%25B0%25E5%2583%25B935%25E8%2590%25AC%3Fmtc%3D60037&d=2uuoLuAEMU6cBVSXjgSp%2BTDyw%2Fr9SRfH8QBX8OZV2FM%3D&h=b15d9bf3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://ps.hket.com/article/2878822/%E5%A4%AA%E5%8F%A4%E5%9F%8E%E7%89%9B%E5%B9%B4%E9%A6%96%E5%AE%97%E6%88%90%E4%BA%A4%20%E5%A5%973%E6%88%BF1780%E8%90%AC%E6%B2%BD%20%E4%BD%8E%E4%BC%B0%E5%83%B935%E8%90%AC?mtc=60037</a><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"x-large\"><strong><span class=\"red\">樓淡:&nbsp;都話買樓唔一定賺架啦! 就算是太古城都唔例外。還是租樓日日(俾業主)賺最好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"db2953eec17f710131b396c2139085c6ae5f4879","tid":2410874,"uid":283240,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-17T03:54:10.000Z","msg":"傻仔做爛市 哩個單位2300萬起跳"},{"pid":"19913482ebe38fbd454c8e253e3ed6a652786992","tid":2410874,"ui